    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-cactus&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with Cactus&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users can&amp;rsquo;t capture audio notes in Aily. When driving or walking, they lose ideas because switching to another app is too slow or unsafe.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-cactus&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with Cactus&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft | Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users can&amp;rsquo;t record audio notes in Aily. When walking with a dog or in other mobile/distracted situations, they want to quickly capture precious ideas by speaking instead of typing. The focus shift to manual typing is slow even though typing itself is fine when undistracted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-cactus-sdk&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with Cactus SDK&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft | Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users can&amp;rsquo;t capture notes while on-the-go (e.g., walking) because typing isn&amp;rsquo;t feasible. They need to speak their thoughts quickly and refine them later.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-26&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft | Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Typing is slow. When I&amp;rsquo;m on a walk with my dog, I can&amp;rsquo;t capture ideas in Aily fast enough. I need a hands-free way to quickly record thoughts that become searchable, editable notes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-cactus&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with Cactus&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft | Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Capturing notes on the go when people can&amp;rsquo;t type, and for people who prefer speaking over typing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-transcription&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with Transcription&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft | Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users lose ideas when they can&amp;rsquo;t type quickly enough to capture them. They need to record audio on the go, transcribe it to text, and turn it into a note without losing the idea in the moment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-transcription&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with Transcription&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Draft | Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users lose ideas while walking because they can&amp;rsquo;t type, and currently have no way to record audio notes that automatically transcribe to text within Aily.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</link>
