      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/guides/local-ai/03-experiments/ideation-skill-experiment/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;ideation-audio-notes-with-on-device-transcription&#34;&gt;Ideation: Audio Notes with On-Device Transcription&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2026-03-27&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Status:&lt;/strong&gt; Ready for PRD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;problem&#34;&gt;Problem&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-problem-are-we-solving&#34;&gt;What problem are we solving?&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users lose ideas when they&amp;rsquo;re on the go and can&amp;rsquo;t type quickly. They need a fast way to capture voice ideas that get converted to searchable text notes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
